@Node "addToSystem()" "commodity/addToSystem"

@{b}   NAME@{ub}
       addToSystem() of @{"commodity" Link "commodity/commodity()"} -- Adds @{"commodity" Link "commodity/commodity()"} to the system.

@{b}   SYNOPSIS@{ub}
       commodity.addToSystem()

@{b}   FUNCTION@{ub}
       The @{"commodity" Link "commodity/commodity()"} is installed by the commodities library, arguments set
       in @{"select()" Link "select()"} will be used. Check self.broker to know if the creation
       was successful or not. There may be an exception for this in the
       future.

@{b}   SEE ALSO@{ub}
       @{"commodity" Link "commodity/commodity()"}

@EndNode

